Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:05.61,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.08,Megumi,,0,0,0,,These shoes are super cute!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:10.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hey so, Megu-chan…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:14.86,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve been slowly making more and more friends too!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:16.86,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve been trying really hard.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:21.10,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That way, one day, I’ll be able to send smiles to you too, Megu-chan.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:23.02,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hm, hm…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:26.31,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But I’m getting further and further ahead, you know?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:30.68,Megumi,,0,0,0,,As long as I’ve got these shoes from you, I feel like I can run to the ends of the earth!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:33.62,Rurino,,0,0,0,,W-Well…!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:36.35,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Then, I’ll just have to go hard, too!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:39.86,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll go abroad and get big!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:43.11,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Then I can take a plane to catch up to you real quick!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:45.21,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:48.89,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And then we can have fun together again!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:50.82,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:53.36,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Let’s have fun together again, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:55.60,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll definitely catch up to you!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.75,0:00:57.21,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:00:59.74,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’ll be waiting!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:05.27,Megumi,,0,0,0,,HelloMegu!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:07.95,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hello to all fifty million soldiers of the Megu Army!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:09.50,Megumi,,0,0,0,,It’s me, Fujishima Megumi!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:11.60,Megumi,,0,0,0,,How are you all today?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:15.86,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did you all miss me~?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:19.36,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s her!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:23.10,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,She was at the Nadeshiko Festival last year…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:26.98,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And she also came to check up on Kozue-senpai when she was in the nurse’s office!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:32.67,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan is my childhood friend.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.90,Rurino,,0,0,0,,She asked me before, actually.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:41.35,Rurino,,0,0,0,,She told me how fun being a school idol was, and that we should do it together.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:43.66,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:45.66,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:49.00,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I’ve never personally seen her with the club at all.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:58.34,Rurino,,0,0,0,,… You know, she just stopped talking about herself at some point.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.79,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Whenever I’d ask, she’d dodge the question.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.98,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I always thought it was kinda weird…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:11.39,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I didn’t think it was because she wasn’t coming to the club anymore…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:14.75,Rurino,,0,0,0,,What happened, Megu-chan…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:25.27,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’ve been super busy editing videos lately, so I haven’t been able to stream much…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:26.44,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Sorry~.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:30.16,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But I’ve been keeping all of you in my thoughts.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.25,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I love you all ☆\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.68,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So when you mentioned going to the second year’s classrooms, Rurino-san…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:43.88,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:47.10,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn’t see her, though.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:49.38,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Or maybe she’s avoiding me…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:55.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And then I almost quit the club before I even saw her…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:03:02.10,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But I’m okay now, because you all accepted me.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:06.85,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So if she has a reason, I’d like to hear it.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:12.56,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan used to always talk about how fun being a school idol is, so...\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:18.08,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Even if I’m a little intimidated to meet with her…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:24.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m sure I’ll be able to help her!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And I…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.32,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I want to be a school idol together with Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.90,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Senpai…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:35.26,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…You’re right.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:39.96,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I should tell you about her, Rurino-san.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:41.04,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:43.45,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Megumi…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:50.47,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Fujishima Megumi-san will most likely not be returning to the School Idol Club.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:51.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh…?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:58.32,Kozue,,0,0,0,,At the Rindo Festival last year, she fell from the stage and suffered an injury.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:02.81,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And although she has already fully recovered from her injury…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:04.39,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Fully recovered…?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:08.51,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I remember hearing that she quit performing because of her injury.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.71,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Then why…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.20,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Megumi is…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:24.77,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Ever since then, whenever she would get up on stage, her legs would freeze up.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.87,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,She couldn’t dance anymore.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:36.02,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,So she stopped being a school idol.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.25,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I… I have to go see her!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.99,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ah, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.61,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,W-We’ll go after her!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:59.00,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So this… is Megumi-senpai’s room?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:03.01,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So you already looked into this, huh, Rurino-san…  \N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:11.22,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan. Megu-chan…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.87,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Open up, please. It’s Ruri.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.27,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.33,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.18,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:26.04,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I didn’t come see you even when you came back to the country.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:30.60,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That’s not really a big deal…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.31,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Why?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.49,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Why didn’t you tell me!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:41.87,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Why didn’t you say anything about getting injured or not being able to dance anymore!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:44.73,Rurino,,0,0,0,,We said we’d be school idols together, didn’t we!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.83,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So why have you been hiding this from me!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:52.91,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…You’ll bother the other students if you shout in the hallway, Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:55.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,M-Megu-chan…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:59.94,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Sorry, there were a bunch of things I had to do this week, so I’m a little tired.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.46,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Kaho-chan, Sayaka-chan…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.27,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes…?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.27,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:09.68,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Your performance at the Nadeshiko Festival was really good.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.19,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Alright, bye.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.48,Rurino,,0,0,0,,M-Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.58,Rurino,,0,0,0,,What about... our…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:33.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve always wanted to be like Megu-chan.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:39.25,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Whenever we tried out new things, she would always run ahead of me.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.25,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’s really strange.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:48.56,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Even back then, whenever I was alone with Megu-chan, I’d never run out of battery.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:53.58,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I decided to study abroad in California because of her.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:07:00.74,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It always seemed like she could run anywhere she wanted to, so I wanted to catch up to her. \N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:11.10,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So I was really happy when she asked me to become a school idol with her.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:16.08,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I thought that I could have fun with Megu-chan again.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:17.92,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But I…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:24.67,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I never even noticed how much she was hurting…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.48,Kaho,,0,0,0,,B-But!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.84,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That’s no way to talk to someone!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:34.08,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You went out of your way to meet with her, and she just shoos you away!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.82,Kaho,,0,0,0,,What kind of long-awaited reunion is that!? So rude!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:38.82,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:44.76,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But, it was also my fault for suddenly showing up, so…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.56,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But, but!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:52.09,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Um… sorry…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.09,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Maybe…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.99,Rurino,,0,0,0,,maybe she doesn’t like school idols anymore…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:02.25,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…I’m not so sure about that.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.25,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.44,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I took a look at Megumi-senpai’s channel.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:14.42,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I noticed she’d uploaded a new video very recently, actually.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:23.96,Megumi,,0,0,0,,With that said, it’s time to look back on the last semester of the Hasunosora School Idol Club!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.87,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Did you know?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:30.98,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Otomune Kozue and Yugiri Tsuzuri finally performed on stage together again!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.59,Megumi,,0,0,0,,It was such an amazing performance, right!?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That wasn’t that long ago…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:46.18,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Megumi-senpai knows quite a lot about you and me, too.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.08,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…So she’s cheering us on?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:56.40,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I believe that if she truly hated the School Idol Club…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:09:02.38,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,She wouldn’t spare all this time and effort to make these videos.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:04.75,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:07.08,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Y’know…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:11.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri-senpai mentioned that it was because of the shock of her accident, right?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.12,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That she’s fully recovered from her injury.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:15.40,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So that means…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:24.50,Rurino,,0,0,0,,If we can motivate her, she might be able to dance again, right?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.64,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Then… I want to try.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
